 Alexander]]\n|UD\n|10\n|25 Feb 2012\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Scottrade Center]], [[St. Louis, Missouri]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|33\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|31\u20132\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Petr Petrov (boxer)|Petr Petrov]]\n|KO\n|4 (12), {{small|2:44}}\n|23 Sep 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|ARG}} {{small|Sociedad Alemana, [[Villa Ballester]], Argentina}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Retained [[WBA (Regular)]] super lightweight title}}\n|-\n|32\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|30\u20132\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|MEX}} [[\u00c9rik Morales]]\n|{{abbr|MD|Majority decision}}\n|12\n|[[\u00c9rik Morales vs. Marcos Maidana|9 Apr 2011]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[MGM Grand Garden Arena]], Paradise, Nevada, U.S.}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Won WBA interim super lightweight title}}\n|-\n|31\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|29\u20132\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Amir Khan (boxer)|Amir Khan]]\n|UD\n|12\n|[[Amir Khan vs. Marcos Maidana|11 Dec 2010]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Mandalay Bay Events Center]], Paradise, Nevada, U.S.}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|For WBA super lightweight title}}\n|-\n|30\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|29\u20131\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[DeMarcus Corley]]\n|UD\n|12\n|28 Aug 2010\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|ARG}} {{small|Estadio Luna Park, Buenos Aires, Argentina}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Retained WBA interim super lightweight title}}\n|-\n|29\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|28\u20131\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|DOM}} [[Victor Cayo]]\n|KO\n|6 (12), {{small|1:38}}\n|27 Mar 2010\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[The Joint (music venue)|The Joint]], [[Paradise, Nevada]], U.S.}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Retained WBA interim super lightweight title}}\n|-\n|28\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|27\u20131\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PAN}} William Gonzalez\n|KO\n|3 (12